    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes works created by the African people of the same name, originally of Fulbe origin, who have assimilated culturally and linguistically with Mande peoples, specifically the Bamana and Maninka.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
